result.name: SNP matrix of 358 domesticated 6-rowed spring barleys from german ex-situ genbank IPK.
result.description: The resequencing of the 358 6-rowed spring barleys provides insights into how barley plant architecture is changed during adaptaion, and will facilitate gene discovery for other traits via GWAS in the future.
result.center: IPK Gatersleben - Leibniz Institute of Plant Genetics and Crop Plant Research
